  "remarks": "Currently Presidential envoy to the North Caucasus Federal District (since 28 August 2016) and aide to Crimean leader Sergey Aksyonov.  Formerly Russia’s Presidential envoy to Crimea.  Former non-permanent member of the Russian Security Council.  Responsible for the implementation of the constitutional prerogatives of the Russian Head of State on the territory of the annexed Autonomous Republic of Crimea.  Former Presidential envoy to the North Caucasus Federal District (August 2016 to June 2018); Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (re-listed on 16 Jun. 2017, 10 June 2020 and 10 June 2023)",
